<plot>American twin brothers, living and working in India have an extreme hatred for each other. Philip has embezzled a bank in India and is running away with intent to escape to America. He runs into his twin, David, on the train to Bombay. When David tries to cut himself in on the stolen money, the enraged Philip kills him. He then changes all his personal belongings, including identification papers, with those of David, since David is not the hunted man. In Bombay, Philip (now David for all intents and purposes)rushes to catch the ship for America. Two detectives stop him and ask for his papers. He satisfies them that he is David and, then, one of the detectives tells him...David, you are under arrest for the murder of your wife. Her body was found an hour ago."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?348737</url></doc>
